// PRAGMA mmap_size — number of bytes the engine may memory-map per database
// file.  0 disables mmap entirely.  Default: SQLITE_DEFAULT_MMAP_SIZE (often
// 0 on most platforms; ~256 MB on others).  Hard cap: SQLITE_MAX_MMAP_SIZE.
// Spec §15.4.
// =============================================================================

